import sys

month = sys.stdin.readline().strip()
day = int(sys.stdin.readline())

if month == "OCT" and day == 31 or month == "DEC" and day == 25:
    print("yup")
else:
    print("nope")

month_dict = {
    "JAN": 1,
    "FEB": 2,
    "MAR": 3,
    "APR": 4,
    "MAY": 5,
    "JUN": 6,
    "JUL": 7,
    "AUG": 8,
    "SEP": 9,
    "OCT": 10,
    "NOV": 11,
    "DEC": 12
}

date = input()

month = date[:3]
day = int(date[4:])

if month_dict[month] == 10 and day == 31 or month_dict[month] == 12 and day == 25:
    print("yup")
else:
    print("nope")
